<title>rfʿẗ ạ̹ydynạ fy mḥḍrk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- rfʿẗ ạ̹ydynạ fy mḥḍrk jwh bytk yạ
 qdyr trfʿ ạlqlwb wtfrḥk wbthzm ạlsẖryr 1- knystnạ ʿrwsẗ lyk dạymaⁿạ frḥạnẗ byk bkẖwr ṣlwạt tsạbyḥ htạfạt ṣrkẖtnạ fy mḥḍrk 2- mhmạ qạmt ḥrwb wạtẖqyn fy ạlmktwb njry wnḥtmy fyk bạ̹ymạn nndh ʿlyk nṣrtnạ fy
 mḥḍrk 3- trfʿnạ llsmạ wnʿysẖ ạ̉jml ḥyạẗ bnsẖwfk yạ yswʿ wbtmsḥ ạldmwʿ dy ṣlạtnạ fy
 mḥḍrk</lyrics>
</song>